---
title: Smart Cheddar and Pork Meatballs with Blueberry BBQ Sauce and Roasted Veggies
description: A sweet and smokey blueberry BBQ sauce is the star of this dinner. It smothers cheddar studded pork meatballs in this 4-star dinner!
